Nov 18 2008 	Nice hotel	My stay in Belvedere hotel was really nice.The location is central, close to Paddington-tube (via the Bakerloo line only 10 minutes to Piccadilly Circus). It's located on a very nice and quiet square (Norfolk square), close to Hyde Park.My room was really ok. The bathroom was not that big, but included everything you need. One negative point: my room was on the fourth floor (so I had to do any steps).The breakfeast was ok (English breakfast).The service of the hotel staff was fine.I will recommend Belvedere hotel to everyone.	
